        <section id="about">
            <h2>Journey to the Past: The Year 1000 CE</h2>
            <p>Welcome to Middle Ages, a groundbreaking historical simulation that transports you back to the year 1000 CE. This is not a game of fantasy or romanticized history. You will face the harsh realities of medieval life, where survival is a daily struggle and the comforts of the modern world are a millennium away.</p>
        </section>
        <section id="historical-context">
            <h2>Life in 1000 CE: A World Apart</h2>
            <p>As you step into the year 1000, you'll find yourself in a world vastly different from our own:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>The Norman Conquest of England is still 66 years away</li>
                <li>The First Crusade won't begin for another 95 years</li>
                <li>The Black Death is more than three centuries in the future</li>
                <li>Most of Europe is ruled by a patchwork of feudal lords</li>
                <li>The Catholic Church dominates spiritual and often political life</li>
                <li>Literacy is rare, and most knowledge is passed down orally</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
        <section id="survival-challenges">
            <h2>Survive Against All Odds</h2>
            <p>In this unforgiving era, you'll face numerous challenges:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Secure food and clean water in a time before modern agriculture and sanitation</li>
                <li>Protect yourself from disease without the benefit of modern medicine</li>
                <li>Navigate complex social hierarchies and avoid running afoul of local powers</li>
                <li>Learn to communicate in a world of diverse dialects and low literacy</li>
                <li>Master period-appropriate skills and trades to earn your place in society</li>
                <li>Endure harsh winters, crop failures, and potential invasions</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="#" class="cta-button">Experience Medieval Survival</a>
        </section>
        <section id="character-creation">
            <h2>Forge Your Medieval Identity</h2>
            <p>In Middle Ages, your character is your lifeline to the past. Our historically accurate character creation system allows you to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Choose from a range of historically appropriate backgrounds and professions</li>
                <li>Customize your appearance based on regional and ethnic characteristics of the era</li>
                <li>Select starting skills that align with your chosen role in medieval society</li>
                <li>Make crucial decisions about your character's religious beliefs and social connections</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Remember, in 1000 CE, your birth often determined your fate. Choose wisely, as your starting position will greatly affect your chances of survival and prosperity.</p>
            <a href="#" class="cta-button">Create Your Medieval Self</a>
        </section>
        <section id="community">
            <h2>Learn and Survive Together</h2>
            <p>Middle Ages is more than just a simulation - it's a community of history enthusiasts, survivalists, and curious minds. Connect with fellow time travelers to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Share survival strategies and historical insights</li>
                <li>Participate in group challenges and historical reenactments</li>
                <li>Discuss the social, economic, and political realities of the era</li>
                <li>Collaborate on historical research to enhance the accuracy of our simulation</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="#" class="cta-button">Join the Community</a>
